txt.en: The Black Blade of Lebennin can manifest painful memories that will bring even the most hardy warrior to ruin.
Defeat the Black Blade of Lebennin while at least one Dol Guldur spirit remains
Defeat the Black Blade of Lebennin while at least one Dol Guldur spirit remains

The Black Blade of Lebennin, along with the Witch-king of Angmar and four of his brethren, oversee the Morgul-host in Osgiliath. All but the Witch-king patrol the city atop their winged fell-beasts - powerful allies to Sauron's servants.
